355
00:26:43,460 --> 00:26:44,420
We'll be able

356
00:26:44,420 --> 00:26:45,700
to watch the stars while enjoying the cool.

357
00:26:52,580 --> 00:26:53,100
What's wrong?

358
00:26:55,460 --> 00:26:56,140
Nothing.

359
00:26:57,500 --> 00:26:59,620
I suddenly realized that

360
00:27:00,220 --> 00:27:02,540
we were actually discussing how to decorate our future home.

361
00:27:03,340 --> 00:27:04,900
I found it surreal for a moment.

362
00:27:06,620 --> 00:27:07,060
Home?

363
00:27:08,500 --> 00:27:10,260
Though we may not stay here for long every year,

364
00:27:10,460 --> 00:27:11,780
it's still our home.

365
00:28:33,180 --> 00:28:33,780
Xiaobai.

366
00:28:40,580 --> 00:28:42,340
I like to hear you say "our home".

367
00:28:52,580 --> 00:28:53,580
I've always liked it.

368
00:29:05,060 --> 00:29:06,140
Greetings, Third Prince.

369
00:29:06,580 --> 00:29:07,100
Chong Lin.

370
00:29:08,180 --> 00:29:09,540
What's the matter with His Majesty?

371
00:29:09,980 --> 00:29:11,620
Why would he appoint Ye Qingti as his successor?

372
00:29:15,940 --> 00:29:17,220
His Majesty felt that he related to

373
00:29:17,460 --> 00:29:19,020
Immortal Qingti the most.

374
00:29:19,700 --> 00:29:20,820
Your Highness, your concern is misplaced.

375
00:30:43,220 --> 00:30:44,260
That's a sign of something.

376
00:30:47,020 --> 00:30:47,500
Chong Lin.

377
00:30:48,100 --> 00:30:49,540
Are you going to try to keep it from me?

378
00:30:50,460 --> 00:30:51,260
