382
00:30:57,300 --> 00:30:58,140
It's too much for me.

383
00:30:58,300 --> 00:30:59,220
You are in charge of things in the Tai Chen Palace.

384
00:30:59,340 --> 00:31:00,580
How could you not know anything?

385
00:31:01,100 --> 00:31:02,220
Even an ordinary man

386
00:31:02,380 --> 00:31:04,580
can't just die suddenly with no reason.

387
00:31:06,300 --> 00:31:06,860
Chong Lin.

388
00:31:07,460 --> 00:31:08,580
After all the twists and turns

389
00:31:08,740 --> 00:31:09,620
Fengjiu and His Majesty have been through,

390
00:31:10,140 --> 00:31:11,980
