391
00:31:12,820 --> 00:31:13,860
If you know anything,

392
00:31:14,620 --> 00:31:15,540
please tell her.

393
00:31:17,020 --> 00:31:17,500
Chong Lin.

394
00:31:18,980 --> 00:31:19,660
Tell her all about it.

395
00:31:26,140 --> 00:31:27,860
I'll begin with the big war

396
00:31:28,020 --> 00:31:29,380
thirty thousand years ago.

397
00:31:30,380 --> 00:31:32,060
Back then, the Demon King Miao Luo was a rebel

398
00:31:32,100 --> 00:31:33,540
against His Majesty who dominated the universe.

399
00:31:34,060 --> 00:31:35,100
So she started killing recklessly,

400
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:36,740
which triggered the war between the gods and the demons.

401
00:31:37,500 --> 00:31:38,980
When His Majesty was sealing Miao Luo,

402
00:31:39,820 --> 00:31:41,580
she left two wisps of Red Qi.

403
00:31:42,260 --> 00:31:44,060
One turned into primordial spirit blood tear

404
00:31:44,980 --> 00:31:46,740
and was sealed in the Forbidden Land in the demons.

405
00:31:48,020 --> 00:31:49,100
While the baby born in

406
00:31:49,500 --> 00:31:50,500
the war between the gods and the demons

407
00:31:50,780 --> 00:31:54,020
was stained with the other Red Qi in her divine sense.

408
00:31:56,780 --> 00:31:59,940
The baby born in that war was....

409
00:32:01,260 --> 00:32:02,140
...was me.

410
00:32:05,500 --> 00:32:05,980
But

411
00:32:06,260 --> 00:32:08,220
