412
00:32:09,660 --> 00:32:11,820
His Majesty found out about your relationship with Miao Luo

413
00:32:12,180 --> 00:32:14,380
in the Dream of Aranya.

414
00:32:27,860 --> 00:32:29,100
Young punk.

415
00:32:29,820 --> 00:32:31,580
You think you can seal me?

416
00:32:34,780 --> 00:32:35,420
Dong Hua.

417
00:32:36,340 --> 00:32:38,420
It's time for us to end this.

418
00:32:39,380 --> 00:32:39,860
Come out!

419
00:32:48,700 --> 00:32:50,100
You finally show up.

420
00:33:18,820 --> 00:33:20,300
Since you want to end this,

421
00:33:21,180 --> 00:33:22,900
I'll put an end to it.

422
00:33:38,820 --> 00:33:40,860
His Majesty knew he couldn't suppress Miao Luo for long.

423
00:33:41,380 --> 00:33:42,100
So for all these years,

424
00:33:42,700 --> 00:33:43,780
he had to reinforce the seal

425
00:33:43,900 --> 00:33:45,260
to prolong the time.

426
00:33:46,780 --> 00:33:47,660
However,

427
00:33:48,260 --> 00:33:49,140
Miao Luo got her power back

428
00:33:49,220 --> 00:33:50,940
way quicker than expected.

429
00:33:53,500 --> 00:33:54,780
Miao Luo was greatly weakened with her power

430
00:33:54,900 --> 00:33:55,900
and sealed by His Majesty.

431
00:33:56,060 --> 00:33:57,540
How did she recover so quickly?

432
00:33:58,140 --> 00:33:59,340
Miao Luo worked her way out step by step.

433
00:34:00,300 --> 00:34:01,460
She first got Lingbi Stone.

434
00:34:01,860 --> 00:34:03,740
Then she got Red Qi back in Fengjiu's body

435
00:34:04,260 --> 00:34:05,940
while the Dream of Aranya was being broken.

436
00:34:07,140 --> 00:34:08,820
Finally, she managed
to get back the demons' holy item, blood tear.

437
00:34:08,940 --> 00:34:10,100
That's why she could break the seal.

438
00:34:10,780 --> 00:34:11,740
At first,

439
00:34:12,340 --> 00:34:13,620
His Majesty and I didn't know about that.

440
00:34:14,980 --> 00:34:15,860
Before the wedding,

441
00:34:16,100 --> 00:34:17,700
Ji Heng coerced His Majesty to meet her

442
00:34:17,700 --> 00:34:19,540
with her father's dragon scale.

443
00:34:20,340 --> 00:34:22,540
Ji Heng wanted to force His Majesty out of marrying you

444
00:34:22,660 --> 00:34:24,460
with dragon scale, which His Majesty couldn't stand.

445
00:34:25,220 --> 00:34:26,940
In the end, he transferred Ji Heng's Qiushui Cold Toxin

446
00:34:27,100 --> 00:34:29,060
all to himself,

447
00:34:29,740 --> 00:34:31,500
so that she could never leave the demons.

448
00:34:32,220 --> 00:34:35,700
But things went wrong with the demons right then.

449
00:34:38,740 --> 00:34:42,140
So His Majesty stayed at the demon clan

450
00:34:43,420 --> 00:34:44,500
not for Ji Heng,

451
00:34:45,540 --> 00:34:46,660
but for Miao Luo.

452
00:34:48,900 --> 00:34:49,540
His Majesty has only loved you

453
00:34:49,740 --> 00:34:51,860
for the whole time.

454
00:34:53,340 --> 00:34:53,780
Your Highness.

455
00:34:54,060 --> 00:34:56,060
Do you know how to remove the Qiushui Cold Toxin quickly?

456
00:34:56,940 --> 00:34:57,900
The quickest approach is to

457
00:34:58,060 --> 00:35:00,660
transfer the toxin all to himself

458
00:35:00,980 --> 00:35:03,260
and then take medicine while cultivating.

459
00:35:03,940 --> 00:35:05,300
That's the approach His Majesty chose.

460
00:35:05,580 --> 00:35:07,220
He'd rather live with toxin

461
00:35:07,300 --> 00:35:08,460
than let the demon princess

462
00:35:08,540 --> 00:35:10,460
bother you in any way.

463
00:35:12,300 --> 00:35:14,940
His Majesty went down to the mortal realm for misfortune

464
00:35:15,460 --> 00:35:17,980
because he spent too much cultivation

465
00:35:18,100 --> 00:35:19,860
when sealing the Miaoyi Chasm.

466
00:35:21,020 --> 00:35:22,980
You know how it went.

467
00:35:23,580 --> 00:35:24,900
His Majesty failed to get all his cultivation back

468
00:35:24,980 --> 00:35:26,380
till the end.

469
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:28,620
From the day he woke up,

470
00:35:28,820 --> 00:35:31,060
he's been preparing for

