497
00:36:42,900 --> 00:36:43,860
You said you would wait until

498
00:36:44,140 --> 00:36:45,820
His Majesty came back and explained to you.

499
00:36:46,260 --> 00:36:47,140
But you might think

500
00:36:47,260 --> 00:36:48,500
His Majesty was so carried away

501
00:36:48,620 --> 00:36:50,020
