510
00:37:19,460 --> 00:37:20,980
Fate Immortal told him that

511
00:37:21,340 --> 00:37:22,660
you and he

512
00:37:22,740 --> 00:37:24,220
were not meant to be

513
00:37:24,420 --> 00:37:26,060
