523
00:37:56,820 --> 00:37:58,020
Shadows have no afterlife.

524
00:37:59,100 --> 00:38:01,260
So the Fate Stone has transferred the destiny
that failed in the shadow couple

525
00:38:01,340 --> 00:38:03,620
