because His Majesty asked the Fate Stone about it.

531
00:38:16,180 --> 00:38:17,900
It's such a pity that

532
00:38:18,140 --> 00:38:20,020
your hard-earned destiny with each other

533
00:38:20,700 --> 00:38:21,820
