540
00:38:43,620 --> 00:38:45,060
Fate Immortal was right.

541
00:38:46,660 --> 00:38:48,060
We were just not meant to be.

542
00:38:49,700 --> 00:38:50,700
Not meant to be.

543
00:38:51,620 --> 00:38:53,860
His Majesty was keeping his relationship with you

544
00:38:54,500 --> 00:38:55,740
